    "TitleKey": "GoblinG_MicroTech_HaulCargo_M_Title",
    "Description": "We\u2019re in need of a hauler with a ship that can transport <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4> for an immediate contract.\n\nYou\u2019ll need to provide your own <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> to handle containers of this size. The cargo is awaiting collection from the freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and should be delivered to a freight elevator at: <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address|ListAll)</EM4>. Bringing <EM4>additional crew to help with the haul is advised</EM4>.\n\nAll the best,\n\n\nAster Remmington\nContractor Liaison Officer\nmicroTech",
